Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99579,102874}{\i1}I never imagined\Nthat this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103583,106878}That's right. I forgot\Nthat girls walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108421,109881}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110298,113092}Oh, no. No need to apologize…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113092,114552}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117305,118848}I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119974,121809}By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122101,125813}I'd like to make it clear there won't be\Nany of that daily diary exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125813,127774}or using a beeper business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128399,130777}Needless to say, there won't be\Nany matching clothes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130777,134739}And birthdays, Christmas,\NValentine's Day…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135531,136532}I don't…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138242,139410}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140578,143373}I don't want anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155843,157595}{\i1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159305,163601}A Formidable Foe?!\NA Mischievous Pixie's Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171526,172568}{\i1}Again…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173444,177031}{\i1}I discovered that this is the house of the\NMysterious Thief Lucifer, a.k.a. Eimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177031,183996}{\i1}Since monitoring this house,\NLucifer hasn't shown any movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183996,186999}{\i1}but her daughter\Nsometimes goes out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:14.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188084,194465}{\i1}And every time she goes out, there's\Nan article about St. Tail the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195383,197427}{\i1}Does this mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199220,202890}Hey! Look! Look at the article\Nabout St. Tail this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203057,205309}She escaped from you again, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205309,207854}Because he has Meimi now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207854,210857}He doesn't care about St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211858,213401}Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213401,215111}Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215111,217280}What kind of logic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217280,218948}Nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218948,221826}I will definitely catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222076,224537}You want to impress Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224537,226205}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226205,228082}Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228082,230293}Why are you jumping\Nto all of these conclusions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231085,233296}How about this, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233713,236632}It's the fortune teller.\NI've heard she is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236632,237550}A fortune teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237550,239761}Oh, yeah. I've heard that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:03.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240178,243514}Yeah, why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245391,247727}That's a cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:13.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247727,253983}What he really wants to know\Nis how their relationship is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254233,256944}Right! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257445,259947}Let it go! Let's change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259947,261616}You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261616,263701}Don't get mad!\NWe're happy for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263701,266913}That's right!\NFinally you two got together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271292,272376}Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273127,275922}How could she, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275922,277840}How could she choose\NAsuka over me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278341,280885}Why? Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280885,283387}Hey! Get away\Nfrom me, Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284514,285807}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288893,290770}It's unusual to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291562,292939}Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293940,296150}I came here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299111,301614}Boy! I can't even have\Na broken heart in peace…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310498,311999}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311999,313292}Nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314418,316462}I'm impressed, Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320007,321008}What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:27.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321884,327139}First of all, those two took\Ntoo long to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327139,330726}Oh, I see. So half of it\Nwas stubborn pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330726,332937}Oh, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336899,339902}I'm sure you'll have\NGod's blessings, Takamiya…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340695,341529}God's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344240,346450}My beautiful face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352582,356168}When I'm hitting him,\NI feel good. That's interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357295,359213}That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:03.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359213,363384}So God's blessings\Nmay not be necessary…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.38,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:363384,365386}Fortune Telling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363676,365386}We've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:09.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365720,369307}This is the fortune teller's house\Nthat Kyoko was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:19.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375021,379275}You aren't interested in this\Nkind of stuff. Let's forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381736,384989}Why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385948,386949}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388242,389911}You want to go in, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392413,393748}Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396959,397710}It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403341,404717}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407094,408679}{\i1}That's the girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409597,412141}Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:01.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416812,421984}Hello. I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422693,424487}Please come by with your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426405,428449}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429116,430952}Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431577,434413}We've heard your fortunes\Nare very accurate…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435498,437917}You want to know whether\Nyou are right for each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437917,439001}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439001,440378}When I see you two, I can tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453557,456227}Your names and dates of birth…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457395,460356}Meimi Haneoka,\Nborn on September 29th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460356,462900}And Asuka Jr. is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462900,465486}Daiki Asuka, August 12th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466070,470449}{\i1}So he is Asuka Jr.,\Nspecial agent for the Mayor…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470908,473411}What are you going to do\Nwith the crystal ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473411,474078}Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498019,498894}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500730,503858}A thick fog is filling the crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504608,506610}So I can't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511741,513826}I've never seen such thick fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514577,517830}And I can see a ring\Naround his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518497,521625}This must be\Nabout the secret promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521625,523502}It's a one-sided promise…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523502,527757}{\i1}What? Is she talking\Nabout St. Tail and Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528257,531802}It seems the ring can\Nnever be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:56.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531802,536015}His character and straightforwardness\Nis indicated in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:09:00.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536015,540686}As a result, this relationship\Nis doomed to failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541645,542438}{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543064,546942}You're hiding something\Nvery big from him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549195,551113}{\i1}I guess I've hit the bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554283,555117}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557661,560206}That's why I hate\Nfortune telling stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560206,562583}She knew things\Nwithout getting any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562917,566295}Listen! That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566295,569048}Those who talk nonsense\Nand tell lies are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570674,571592}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573177,574720}{\i1}Honest eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576055,577890}{\i1}Irremovable ring…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579350,582186}All right, then.\NLet's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582645,585189}I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586190,590444}{\i1}That's the sign that he can't\Nforgive people who deceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590444,593656}{\i1}I'm sure he won't forgive\Nmy being St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594990,596659}I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597409,599620}That's a solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600454,603582}Yesterday, a person\Nnamed Sakiko visited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604166,606585}She valued it a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607586,608462}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:13.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609547,613884}You know about Pandora, the fortune\Ntelling place, don't you, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613884,615553}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615553,618889}Sakiko went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622226,623644}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623644,625396}My statue of Mary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625396,626689}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:32.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626689,632611}That solid-gold statue of Mary\Nis bringing you misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632611,634321}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:41.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636574,641871}You can bring the solid-gold statue\Nof Mary to us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641871,644248}We'll take full responsibility\Nfor its disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645166,647251}You've got to be kidding!\NHow could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647960,650713}Are you prepared\Nto have misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652673,654800}I can't do it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656719,658220}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662850,665686}So did she give it away? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:11.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665686,671192}I suppose the fortune teller\Nuses hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671192,672651}Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672651,676655}So Sakiko can't go to the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677281,678574}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678574,680159}– I went there.\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680159,684121}I went to the fortune teller\Nand she gave me a scary fortune…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:30.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685039,690085}If Asuka Jr. finds out I'm St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690586,692796}You've been deceiving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695674,696717}Let's stop stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699428,700387}Seira…
Comment: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:42.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,702723}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:47.72,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:707728,707728}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709313,710689}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:54.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710981,714235}I appreciate what you\Nhave done very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:12:01.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714985,721116}But you don't need to see\NAsuka Jr. as St. Tail anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722159,723661}So let's end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726538,728624}I love you. I love you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729124,731585}No! We can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731585,733587}We can't desert those\Npeople who are in trouble…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734964,736548}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737883,740761}We have to get back\Nthe solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744098,747726}Now it's lunch time!\NLunch time! Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748102,750354}You brought a lunchbox\Ntoday, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751647,752690}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755901,760072}It's been a while since St. Tail\Nbooby-trapped your lunchbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:46.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761490,766120}"Tonight I'll get the\Nsolid-gold statue of Mary. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,771000}Oh, boy! She really\Nwent all out on this lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771000,772084}I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773502,776755}Hey, Haneoka.\NLook at Asuka's lunchbox…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776964,779842}– Stop it!\N– Then let us eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779842,781218}Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783095,786181}{\i1}Let me make lots and lots\Nof whatever you like…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:10.60,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:786181,790602}{\fad(0,2000)}Cookbook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:11.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787349,791770}Whatever happens from this point,\NI hope I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:22.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798902,802614}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807536,808620}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810873,812291}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814168,816920}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830517,831602}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833228,835397}Please tell me\Nwhen things get too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836065,837566}Please promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838192,839651}If it happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840903,844531}If it happens,\NI will become St. Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846075,848494}{\i1}St. Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:10.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850120,850996}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851455,852289}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852748,854375}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859004,860923}Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863008,866887}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876063,877773}A solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878440,880067}We don't have any…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880067,882111}All we have are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884321,886949}It's made of solid gold…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886949,888992}Our store doesn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888992,890202}I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.66,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:890202,892663}Sakurai Jewelers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894623,897668}We don't have such a thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898585,900671}A solid-gold statue of Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901004,904591}Our store doesn't have it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904591,905634}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906552,907636}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:12.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907928,912599}That St. Tail! Where is it?\NWhere is the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913142,917563}Where in the world is there\Na solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921525,923777}Mysterious Thief St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925737,927739}{\i1}I'm sorry, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:31.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927739,931577}{\i1}I didn't want you here…\Nwhere she is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936081,938834}I came to get\Nthe statue of Mary back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941044,944047}You came here.\NThat's what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944047,946175}I have several things\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946175,948635}Now watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950179,952014}Doesn't this smell nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953849,956602}Now take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958395,959980}{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961398,963066}This fragrance is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966361,967529}The smell in a bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968155,969740}It's lavender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974703,976663}Your date of birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978749,980125}September…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980667,982628}29th…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984755,986256}I've heard it somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988258,990761}What is your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990761,992304}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992304,993889}Genichiro…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993889,995307}And mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996183,997684}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997684,998894}Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001480,1004024}Are you the daughter\Nof the Mysterious Thief Lucifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005150,1006652}Meimi Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008070,1009530}You're Meimi Haneoka, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009530,1012491}You are\Nthe Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012491,1013909}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017829,1019373}Meimi Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020582,1022042}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022042,1023877}Are you St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024086,1025379}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026547,1027381}You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027589,1029049}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029049,1030342}Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031969,1033554}Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035722,1037975}Yes. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038809,1041270}I've been hiding it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041812,1044273}I was scared that you'd find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045983,1047568}I was scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048694,1051196}I was really scared…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054324,1055701}Okay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057411,1060664}I just wanted to know your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060831,1063667}You said some\Nunexpected things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066587,1068589}Ms. Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069965,1071550}What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072092,1075053}I was hypnotized?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075596,1077014}{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078932,1082603}I can't have my secret\Nrevealed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082603,1084438}I wouldn't be able\Nto continue my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085063,1087441}– Your business?\N– That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088025,1092404}Stealing people's valuables?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097367,1098702}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:23.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098702,1103332}I'm not planning to reveal\Nyour identity to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103749,1107377}Let me tell you what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107377,1108295}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:33.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108587,1113258}I'm thinking of taking revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114259,1116386}Lucifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116386,1117220}My mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118055,1119222}On my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120515,1124353}Then I'll take the statue\Nof Mary, Ms. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125687,1127522}You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127856,1129775}One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129775,1130984}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141620,1143705}Oh, the statue of Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143705,1145374}It isn't hot…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147334,1148335}Was it magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156134,1159304}I'll take the statue of Mary,\NMs. Fortune Teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159888,1161306}How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161473,1162683}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172192,1173193}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175320,1176905}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179825,1183620}{\i1}I wonder what will happen\Nif she continues with that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184287,1185747}{\i1}Her hypnosis…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187416,1189209}You're Meimi Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190585,1193714}{\i1}I have to stop her hypnosis…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193714,1196091}{\i1}At the time, my body got cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196842,1200053}{\i1}I thought the real Asuka Jr.\Nwas asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202973,1204307}{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210689,1213984}The solid-gold statue\Nof Mary was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214526,1216945}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216945,1220991}It was the most valuable item\Nout of everything we've gotten recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220991,1223201}– Maju.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:28.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223201,1228373}Lucifer is living a normal life.\NIt won't be fun to make her suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228373,1229916}Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230292,1232419}What? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232961,1236423}And the daughter's pain\Nis her mother's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236423,1238383}Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238759,1240719}Yes! I'm with you all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240719,1242345}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:47.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243555,1247309}We can have\Nmore fun that way, Maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248518,1250896}The Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250896,1252981}The battle is just now starting…
