Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.91,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1268246,1270916}Let me dream of a melody,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:15.96,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1270916,1275962}'cause something tells me\Nwe won't stay like that for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:23.42,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1275962,1283428}The future is like a rainbow,\Na tunnel of vibrant colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:27.76,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1283428,1287766}and I'm stepping right inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.15,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1295106,1298151}The night after our mysterious date
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.15,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1299027,1303156}I get so lonely you wouldn't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:50.70,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1303615,1310705}Under my eyelids there's only image of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:54.29,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1310705,1314292}I want to remodel this romance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:57.54,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1314417,1317546}and forget about yesterday already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.00,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1318213,1322008}Let's stop holding back and get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.88,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1322008,1325887}Can you hear the beat of my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.55,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1326888,1329558}Let this sweet melody continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:14.43,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1329558,1334437}Even if our love is shaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:21.69,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1334437,1341695}or we stray from the rainbow,\Nthere's not a day I'd rewind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:28.36,saint tail ed en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1341987,1348368}You see, my tears have dried long ago.
